draft install instructions
===============================

install basic ruby environment:

  sudo apt-get install ruby1.8 rake rubygems libmysql-ruby mysql-server

prevent rubygems from installing rdoc (optional):

  cat > ~/.gemrc
  gem: --no-rdoc --no-ri

install required gems:

  cd crabgrass-core
  sudo gem install rails --version='~>2.3'
  mkdir log
  touch log/development.log
  sudo rake gems:install

create the database:

  sudo mysqladmin create crabgrass_development
  rake db:schema:load
  rake db:fixtures:load

install helper applications:

  sudo apt-get install graphicsmagick

run server:

  INFO=1 BOOST=1 script/server
